REPLACE with a brief description of the study, population, and goals.

SITE
----
REPLACE with data acquisition site and scanner information.

SESSIONS
--------
Session 01: Resting-state fMRI, T1w, fieldmaps, DWI
Session 02: Resting-state fMRI, T1w, hippocampal T2w, fieldmaps

TASKS
-----
task-rest: Eyes-open resting-state fMRI

DATA COLLECTION
---------------
REPLACE with IRB protocol number, consent information, and any
relevant acquisition notes.

PREPROCESSING
-------------
Raw DICOMs were converted to BIDS format using dcm2bids 3.2.0.
Anatomical images were defaced using PyDeface prior to sharing.
Preprocessing was performed using fMRIPrep 25.2.5.
Quality control reports were generated using MRIQC 24.0.2.

DATA ORGANIZATION
-----------------
This dataset follows the Brain Imaging Data Structure (BIDS)
specification v1.11.1. See https://bids.neuroimaging.io for details.

Pipeline scripts are located in code/.

